ZXASCII
AUTO -1
PROG plasma6
10 REM Plasma Peter!
20 RADIANS: WINDOW DEPTH 0,32: CLS 0: SCREEN LOCK 
30 RESTORE : FOR f=1 TO 5: READ ii,im,st: FOR j=1 TO 600: GO SUB 50: WAIT SCREEN: INC ii,111: NEXT j: NEXT f: GO TO 30
40 DATA 1,1,0.01,0.4,0.4,0.02,0.7,0.7,0.01,0.5,0.5,0.04,1,1,0.05,1,1.5,0.02
50 LET fx=0: FOR x=0 TO 319: LET i=1: LET fy=0: FOR y=0 TO 319: PLOT INK i*(1+COS(fx))+i*(1+COS(fy));x,y: LET i=i*im+ii: INC fy,st: NEXT y: INC fx,st: NEXT x: RETURN 
